Class Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course.Activity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Conflict
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Course, Event
    public abstract class Activity
extends java.lang.Object
implements Conflict
    Abstract class for Courses and Events which contains the mutual fields and methods between the two subclasses Will be used to make up the schedule in WolfScheduler
    Author:
    Yash Agarwal
